It seems that the permission "Page/Create" also restricts editing. I would have assumed that "Page/Create" controlled whether or not a user or group could add a new page to a space. But it also seems to restrict whether or not a user or group can edit pages within a space. Possible resolutions...

1) This permission should be split up so that page creation and page editing are seperate.
2) The permission should be renamed "Create/Edit" to reflect that this controls both creation and editing of pages.

